issue.title: How to create room and chat
issue.body:
I am able to create room I'd is created but while using name text nickname all are not storing 
Please help me out

comment.body:
First change to the api directory

```
cd chat-api
```

Then start the database

```
npm run dc:up:mongo
```

Then start the server api

```
npm run start
```
